description:
Supported Platforms:
• NETFramework


Rapidly develop robust, accurate, and extremely fast OCR and Forms Recognition and Processing applications that extract text and data from document images. With OCR technology, users can extract text from images or converts images to text-searchable and editable formats such as PDF, PDF/A, DOC, DOCX, RTF, HTML, MOBI, ePUB, XLS, EMF, XML, AltoXML, and XPS. LEADTOOLS can recognize characters in more than 40 languages. This package includes English, Spanish, French, Italian, and German. For more languages, see the Leadtools.Ocr.Languages.* packages. 

The advanced OCR technology in LEADTOOLS is multi-faceted and can be used as a standalone feature as well as the driving force behind more advanced technologies such as forms recognition, check recognition, and document conversion. With as few as three lines of code, you can convert images to text-searchable documents. 

This is just a small part of a large technology offering called LEADTOOLS. To see all that LEADTOOLS has to offer, go to https://www.leadtools.com

Example Projects:
• OCR, Forms Recognition, and Forms Processing - https://bitly.im/leadtools_ocr
• All - https://bitly.im/leadtools_all



Example Projects:
